[I] The pattern matching swiss knife

[T] YARA is a tool aimed at (but not limited to) helping malware researchers
[T] to identify and classify malware samples. With YARA you can create
[T] descriptions of malware families (or whatever you want to describe)
[T] based on textual or binary patterns.

[U] https://virustotal.github.io/yara/

